stories.title: Mujeeb's maiden five-for seals Afghanistan's series win
stories.subTitle: Afghanistan v Zimbabwe, 4th ODI, Sharjah
stories.seoTitle: Mujeeb's maiden five-for seals Afghanistan's series win
stories.summary: The mystery spinner did the bulk of the damage as Zimbabwe collapsed to 134 all out. It only took Afghanistan 21.1 overs to chase that down without loss, with Mohammad Shahzad and Ihsanullah making unbeaten half-centuries
